movie.title: K2
movie.plot: They call it the savage mountain. 27 people have perished trying to reach the summit on K2, the world's second highest peak. A U.S. climbing team, funded by millionaire Clairborne is determined to conquer K2.

movie.title: Kajaki
movie.plot: British soldiers guarding the Kajaki Dam set out to rescue a three-man team after one of them loses a leg to a landmine.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 BAFTA Film Award. Another 4 wins & 6 nominations.
